name: Super Star Wars: Return of the Jedi
overview: Join the Rebellion and crush the Death Star in a giant 16-meg universe filled with all the action and adventure of the Star Wars finale. The command of five different characters-- from Wicket the Ewok to Princess Leia--and go up against the Empire's worst, from Jabba the Hutt to the Emperor himself! This is it! You're going to need every ounce of Force you're got in you.
